BT /F2 14 Tf 54 712.0 Td (Introduction) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 690.0 Td (Migraines are not 'just headaches.' They are a complex neurological condition affecting) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 676.0 Td (over 1 billion people worldwide. This workbook helps you identify your personal triggers,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 662.0 Td (track attack patterns, develop rescue protocols, and work toward fewer, less severe) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 648.0 Td (migraine days.) Tj ET
endstream
